OL,5, Firms including Apple, Disney and IBM  
OL,6, have paused advertising on X amid an   
OL,7, antisemitism storm on the site.        
OL,9,FIt comes after X owner Elon Musk       
OL,10,Famplified an antisemitic trope on the  
OL,11,Fplatform formerly known as Twitter.    
OL,13,FThe boycott has also been picking up   
OL,14,Fsteam in the wake of an investigation  
OL,15,Fby a US group which flagged ads        
OL,16,Fappearing next to pro-Nazi posts on X. 
OL,18,FMr Musk has denied his post was        
OL,19,Fantisemitic and has threatened to sue  
OL,20,Fover the advertising investigation.    
